title: "Stunspot's Guide to AI Systems: The AI Engineering Systems Canon"
abstract: >-
  A Markdown-native knowledge repository built primarily to support
  AI-assisted design, engineering, analysis, evaluation, and
  decision-making across modern AI systems. Organized across 12 volumes
  and 37 reports (AI-ENG-A through AI-ENG-AK), spanning model steering,
  context architecture, corpus engineering, retrieval, model lifecycle,
  runtime mechanics, agents, tools, multimodal interfaces, security,
  resilience, evaluation, telemetry, governance, product architecture,
  and system doctrine.
